observationTitle: Longer-term (e.g., 1 month or more) travel to a JE-endemic area
indicationText: Administer to persons who plan for longer-term (e.g., 1 month or more) travel to JE-endemic areas.
clarifyingText: Endemic Area and transmission season is determined by country.  Refer to the yellow book for a definition of the transmission season: http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/travel/yellowbook/2014/chapter-3-infectious-diseases-related-to-travel/japanese-encephalitis
